snippet.textDisplay:
Marketing team for Coke studio season 15 should be fired. No one has been able to create the hype after the record-breaking season 14. 

By the way, season 14 started off with a bang, with Abida Parveen's Tu Jhoom... And this season started off with a complete dud. I'm all for diversity and celebrating different culture, but the starting is so important. 

 Coke Studio has completely missed the mark in my opinion. Hopefully, this season gets better as more artists are revealed. 

By the way, where is the artist reveal? Where is the season promo? Marketing team has been a complete letdown. Total embarrassment.
